    "testimonials": {
      "type": "custom-liquid",
      "settings": {
        "custom_liquid": "<div class=\"page-width\" style=\"text-align:center;\">\n  <p style=\"font-size:11px;font-weight:600;letter-spacing:0.1em;text-transform:uppercase;color:#f4a51c;margin-bottom:4px;\">Customer stories</p>\n  <h2 style=\"font-family:'Poppins',sans-serif;font-size:18px;font-weight:600;margin:0 0 8px;\">What our buyers say</h2>\n  <p style=\"font-size:13px;color:#666;margin-bottom:24px;\">Real feedback from real Furniva customers</p>\n\n  <div style=\"display:flex;gap:16px;overflow-x:auto;justify-content:center;\">\n    <div style=\"background:#F7F5F1;border-radius:12px;overflow:hidden;max-width:320px;flex-shrink:0;text-align:left;\">\n      <div class=\"fv-review-image-trigger\" data-review-modal=\"fv-review-img-1\" style=\"cursor:pointer;\">\n        <img src=\"{{ 'review-santosh-1.png' | asset_url }}\" alt=\"Customer photo - Furniva Skyline Two Door Shoe Rack, Wenge\" style=\"width:100%;height:200px;object-fit:cover;display:block;\">\n      </div>\n      <div style=\"padding:18px;\">\n        <div style=\"color:#f4a51c;font-size:14px;margin-bottom:8px;\">&#9733;&#9733;&#9733;&#9733;&#9733;</div>\n        <div style=\"font-size:14px;font-weight:700;color:#152420;margin-bottom:6px;\">Great DIY product you will enjoy making</div>\n        <p class=\"fv-review-text\" style=\"font-size:13px;color:#3a3a3a;line-height:1.7;margin-bottom:6px;max-height:66px;overflow:hidden;\">Getting this DIY shoe rack was a decision I'll always remember! The product came earlier than designated ETA and came with good packaging in good condition. There was a small instruction page which helped to build the rack easily. The only problem was that it had exact number of screws, if anything missed could make problem but fortunately I handled carefully. It took around 2 hours for me to assemble but it was fun. The end result is really great!! Good and I'd definitely recommend!</p>\n        <button type=\"button\" class=\"fv-review-toggle\" style=\"background:none;border:no